  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd  \u0b86\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0ba4\u0bc2\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Upholding the rule of law is essential to stabilizing the economy - US ambassador",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "In a meeting with Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardena, US Ambassador Julie Chung emphasized that maintaining access to justice and the rule of law is essential for stabilizing and rebuilding the economy, including negotiations with the International Monetary Fund.",
        "US Ambassador Julie Chung had made this meeting to congratulate Dinesh Gunawardena on his inauguration as Prime Minister.",
        "He said the above in a post made on his Twitter page regarding the meeting with the Prime Minister.",
        "\"I met Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardena to discuss ways in which the United States can help the people of Sri Lanka during these challenging times.",
        "It is necessary to maintain access to justice and the rule of law, while carrying out negotiations with the International Monetary Fund and taking steps to stabilize the economy.' mentioned that.",
        "US Ambassador Julie Chung met President Ranil Wickremesinghe on Wednesday and said, 'The United States will continue to provide cooperation to Sri Lanka to promote good governance that respects human rights and listens to the aspirations of the people.' It is noteworthy that it was mentioned."
      ],
